Library
-------

Configure the library:

 $ ./autogen.sh --prefix=/path/to/installation/directory

Build the library:

 $ make all

Install the library:

 $ make install

The libraries are now located in the
/path/to/installation/directory/lib/opensand/plugins directory

Documentation
-------------

HTML documentation can be generated from the source code thanks to Doxygen:

 $ make doc

Open the ./doc/html/index.html file in your favorite web browser.

If you want to clean the documentation:

 $ make clean-doc


See the installation manual on OpenSAND website (www.opensand.org) for more details
